WEBVTT

00:00:28.040 --> 00:00:32.896
She faced the barrage of hate words
with the power of her own sane ones.

00:00:32.920 --> 00:00:36.600
TED Talks India welcomes Gurmehar Kaur.

00:00:37.958 --> 00:00:42.358
(Applause)

00:00:47.800 --> 00:00:50.336
Gurmehar Kaur: My name
is Gurmehar Kaur.

00:00:50.340 --> 00:00:55.446
My father was an army man,
who sacrificed his life for the country.

00:00:55.480 --> 00:00:58.060
You may have heard about me,

00:00:58.060 --> 00:01:03.736
possibly on Facebook, WhatsApp, Twitter, 
chain messages or on prime time debates.